I'm sorry to hear about the billing issue. It sounds like there might be a misunderstanding with the billing process. Could you please check if there's an outstanding balance from previous campaigns? If not, I recommend reaching out to our support team at adsupport@newsbreak.com with your screenshots and details of the issue. They'll be able to investigate further and assist you.

It sounds like you're experiencing an issue with being billed despite not having any active campaigns or ads. Let's try to figure this out! Could you please check if there are any pending or paused campaigns that might be causing the billing? Also, ensure that there are no scheduled campaigns set to start soon. If everything seems correct and you're still facing this issue, I recommend reaching out to our support team at adsupport@newsbreak.com with the details and screenshots for further assistance.

It sounds like you're experiencing an issue with being billed despite not having any active campaigns or ads. Let's try to figure this out. Could you please check the following details for me?

1. **Billing History**: Review your billing history to see if there are any charges that don't match your campaign activity.
2. **Campaign Status**: Double-check the status of your campaigns to ensure none are accidentally set to active.
3. **Ad Account Settings**: Verify if there are any automated settings or subscriptions that might be causing charges.

If everything seems correct and you're still unsure why you're being billed, I recommend reaching out to our support team at adsupport@newsbreak.com with the details and screenshots for further assistance.

I'm sorry to hear that you're being billed without any active campaigns or ads. To resolve this, please check the following:

1. **Ad Set Level**: Ensure that there are no ad sets with active budgets.
2. **Campaign Level**: Verify that no campaigns are accidentally set to active.
3. **Account Settings**: Double-check your account settings for any recurring billing options.

If everything seems correct and you're still experiencing issues, I recommend reaching out to our support team at adsupport@newsbreak.com with details of your account and the issue. They will be able to assist you further.
